reviewText: This video is awesome. If you are just starting to exercise this is the best video. Easy, and fun to follow. It will make you sweat but you can modify how hard you want to work out.
I like this video a lot, is very easygoing and nice for me.  But is time to put it in CD, since VHS is not any more in some homes.
I enjoyed this exercise video very much. Its ability to trasmit this amount of knowledge in such an understandable manner is remarkable. It was fun and educational.
